1) Double Click the My Project item in the Solution Explorer.
2) Click the Publish tab.
3) Note the Version Number information.
4) Click the Updates Button.
5) Change the Specified Min. Version Number to Match the Verison number information.
6) Open the AssemblyInfo.vb file.
7) Change the version information to the latest version.
8) Save the project.
9) Double Click the My Project item in the Solution Explorer.
10) Click Publish Now.
11) Save the project again.
12) Commit to SVN the released version.